{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"572aeec9b5","title":"毛泽东对山西省委关于整顿和巩固人民公社的决议的批语和注文","origin":"根据文件的翻印件打印","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"6f63949daf","index":0,"year":1959,"month":2,"day":28,"articleId":"572aeec9b5"}],"tags":[{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e759231f2d","name":"农业战线","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-dayuejin","name":"中国大跃进-大饥荒数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-dayuejin":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"e7cae6719a","type":"title","text":"毛泽东对山西省委关于整顿和巩固人民公社的决议的批语和注文","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"572aeec9b5"},{"id":"258c4497c1","type":"subtitle","text":"一","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"572aeec9b5"},{"id":"e22bd0e5e1","type":"paragraph","text":"即刻印发各同志。这是一个好文件，值得一读，借作参考。这里印的，斩头去尾，第一节、第六节、第七节略去了，中间二、三、四、五段，是精华。着重地读第三、第四、第五节，是讲得很好的。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"572aeec9b5"},{"id":"6af77ee506","type":"paragraph","text":" 毛泽东1959年2月28日。于郑州。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"572aeec9b5"},{"id":"4559f79d0c","type":"subtitle","text":"二","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"572aeec9b5"},{"id":"34187f4de5","type":"paragraph","text":"毛注：这里应当加一句：又应当批判只顾国家和公社大集体、而不顾生产队小集体和社员个人(全国共有几亿人口之多)，公社积累过多、社员分配过少，社办县办工业过多因而抽去人力过多，使生产队人力过少、妨碍农业任务完成等“左”倾冒险主义思想；必需承认，目前实际上还是基本的队有制、部分的社有制。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"572aeec9b5"},{"id":"8604042afe","type":"subtitle","text":"三","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"572aeec9b5"},{"id":"51ad40000b","type":"paragraph","text":"毛注：农业应放在第一位，要占有最大部分劳动力，在没机械化以前，应当如此。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"572aeec9b5"},{"id":"0e0b59bc7b","type":"subtitle","text":"四","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"572aeec9b5"},{"i